Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.22,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry. There's\Nnothing more to it, though."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:04.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll apologize to everyone. I don't\Nthink there's anything else I can do."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.47,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't have to apologize."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's true, you weren't exactly\Nthe right person for the job."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's remarkable that\Nyou've done this much."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.15,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll think of some way\Nto deal with it now."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:20.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,"But even if it does go well, it probably\Nwon't go in the direction you wanted."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:21.77,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Send"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:22.81,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sent"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.24,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here:\NSorry to bring this up out of the blue."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.66,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪: Sorry, there's no getting\Naround the time and distance."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:32.33,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not at all. Given the situation,\Nthere's nothing you can do about it."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.12,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪: It's a request from my\Ndear {\i1}kohai{\i0}. I wish I could do something."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:42.15,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you have any other ideas?\NAbout anyone who would be able to?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.80,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪: Hmm."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:45.83,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-e-♪:"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.25,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please insert name here: Senpai?"
