Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:51.58,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"They're the Classic Lit Club, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:56.03,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I would be delighted if you brought\Nall the club members with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:02.42,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom
