Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:18.63,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:24.15,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
